   551	the prefix by the untracked contract (documented). Determinism of read
   552	order across pure retries is the same purity fact positional caching
   553	already required (C14). Fallback if prefix compares ever measure hot
   554	(they are int compares over short arrays): a whole-run stamp — coarser,
   555	still sound, more refetches — is the degenerate configuration, flagged,
   556	not default.
